Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:49.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:54.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.95,0:00:56.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:06.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:24.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:30.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:35.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:37.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:44.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:56.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:02:01.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.97,0:02:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous ahead of here!\NWater is rushing towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't you guys hear the sound of water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if the water flows into\Nan underground passage like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have no choice but to drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-kun, can't you hear the sound of water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, it's true that\Nsomething doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stop, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other passage. We have\Nno choice but to keep on this path!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Granny and the others\Nare being chased by water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Pirate guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Do something about this water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work! The Bone Balloon is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Giant Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Giant Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.27,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol...! Pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick... Victory Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron outer shell got cracked...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship won't last long!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close. I almost got split in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Mystical Mermaid Appears?\NAs Consciousness Fades Away..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shrinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they fire at their\Nown battleship? Are they idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in any case, I got shrunk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear is such an interesting\Nidea and it's really powerful,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but how my body reacts is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was pumped up for about a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably stay shrunk for about a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.54,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hide until I go\Nback to normal or I'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if he's serious or fooling around...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be disappointing if he died from\Na small cannon attack like that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can now see the main island front gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky, the one you love so much,\Nhas been taken away just like Tom-san was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat was going on a rampage\Non that battleship just a bit ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now he's been blown to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you guys right! Your captain has died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey... They fired at the ship\Nwhile their own men were on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power of a Buster Call,\Nthe attack I set in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is justice, Cutty Flam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hand Nico Robin over to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, I could make your charges go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to protect\Nthat woman in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you'd trust that dangerous\Nwoman who carries Ohara blood in her veins
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,over the World Government that\Nprotects you ordinary people every day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you disobey us,\Njust like Tom, you'll end up dy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My face can't get any more swollen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it! I've heard enough of your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drew the elephant sword, Funkfreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing is powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Funkfreed. To ensure they\Nwon't be able to resist any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll fatally wound Nico Robin,\Nwhose guard is down right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Elephant Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so pathetic in every respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.30,0:09:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funkfreed! You're an elephant!\NYou shouldn't be losing to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go crazy and cut them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your nose back to normal, elephant,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless you want me to shoot\Nyou right between the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. That's good. You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin, will Straw Hat\Nand the others come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will... for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spandam, I thought I told you that\NI'm betting everything on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought a day like this would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had had power on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm changing the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the charge of building the pirate ship\Nfor Gold Roger, King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll take shipbuilding\Nengineer Tom to Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What got into that old geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I don't have\Nbusiness with his disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release those two disciples!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tom-san can no longer be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the World Government we're\Nup against, there's nothing we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear it. Tom-san saved you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make an enemy of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how many lives\Nyou have, it's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enies Lobby is the judicial island\Nowned by the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No criminals taken there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have ever returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep going; give him what he wants.\NDon't be concerned about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Puffing Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking your creator to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit, ribbit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you pass here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Tom-san back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get Tom-san back at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who know the myth of\Nthe impregnable Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who know the power\Nof the World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats overturn their\Ncommon sense and advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to rescue one friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they make the world into their\Nenemy without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exhilarating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to this very day, I've never once\Nforgotten about Tom-san's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid face of that official...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time it went through my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I hoped...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hoped that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, you idiot! Stop it! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one day I'd be able to crush him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.96,0:13:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them, my wish came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm someone who once died in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it enables the Straw Hats\Nto leave this place alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind sacrificing my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over the escort ship to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare an escape route for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight, too. I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with all your might!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you stay on the island!\NSail out on my raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Saul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it for me. I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! There's no one on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alone now, but you'll\Nmeet friends someday for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The sea is vast, so someday, definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll come across friends who'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Robin! Don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live together with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is different from Ohara... From that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because... I'm not... alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance to Enies Lobby...\NThe main gate is around the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Giants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to get off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about it--were you\Nimpressed by our giant guts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.81,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They arrived here ahead of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! They really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we tied them up in the courthouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Aim at them.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After stating your unit and marine code
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and showing your picture ID,\Nyou may board the battleship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief. I thought we were gonna\Nget eliminated along with the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resisting is futile, pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make one move, and we'll fire\Nour guns and cannons at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.82,0:17:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure doesn't seem like\Nthey're gonna let us get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind us is a harbor and an island on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no place to escape, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of us are guns and cannons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you thinking about right now, Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell that we're headed to now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ribbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished retrieving marines and officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all battleships.\NMaintain a distance from the main gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite an unbalanced\Ncombat power you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.82,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should willingly accept it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if that's the price you pay\Nfor the power you used earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Return. Paper Art. Fighting Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:18:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, your ridiculous attacks wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but die in that stupid state, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol! Spots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to normal, body!\NHurry! Hurry! I'm gonna be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damage I took earlier is affecting my legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm going back...!\NI'm going back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? My attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did a number on you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something...! Or we'll all drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we still haven't really\Ngotten Robin-chan back yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this it? My life...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was quite fun... Hey!\NI haven't lived long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it wouldn't even be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the great Usopp, brave warrior\Nof the sea, died from drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold my breath any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe...! Everything's going dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine. Get ahold of yourselves!\NI'm not gonna let you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is being pulled by something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several sailors are drowning in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As their consciousness fades away,\Nthey see an elegant tail fin...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they look up, they see\Nlong hair swaying in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mermaid legend...\NIt's like we're seeing a fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm dreaming... please don't let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wake...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go super express!\NMake sure you hold your breath tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.02,0:22:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Du...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Du...\N--Du...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.53,0:22:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Du... A dugong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth... is this Buster Call thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry up, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends... Your friends...\Nare waiting for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cannon Fire Sinks the Island!\NFranky's Lamentation"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
